            <div type="apparatus">
                <ab>1–2. Presumably for <w lemma="*κοντροκυνήγιος">*κοντροκυνήγιος</w>, a wild-beast hunter with a pike. LSJ lists <w lemma="κοντροκυνηγέσιον">κοντροκυνηγέσιον</w>, citing IGRR 4.1632 and SEG 6.608, where L. Robert refers to his discussion of IGRR 3.360 in Rev.Arch. 30 (1929) 29–31 = Opera Minora Selecta 1.696–698. There he comments on the use of <w lemma="σιδηροκόντρα">σιδηροκόντρα</w>. There are no literary occurrences recorded in TLG. Cf. the fragmentary T12.6 for another possible occurrence at Smyrna.</ab>
            </div> 
